{"nodes": [{"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_document", "label": "Design", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_context", "label": "Context", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "pi-vimmode already documents core behavior in `README.md`, but feature breadth has grown across modes, search, Ex substitution, registers, marks, macros, rendering, lifecycle, and settings. Settings are implemented in `src/config.ts` and typed in `src/types.ts`; behavior contracts live across existing OpenSpec specs and tests. New docs must make those sources easier for users to consume without changing runtime code or configuration. User-facing docs will live in `docs/features.md` and `docs/set"}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_goals_non_goals", "label": "Goals / Non-Goals", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 7", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "**Goals:** - Create a complete feature guide with useful examples for every pi-vimmode feature area."}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_decisions", "label": "Decisions", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 23", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "1. **Use `docs/features.md` and `docs/settings.md` for user guides.** - Rationale: Feature and settings references are user-facing manuals, not architecture decisions. - Alternative considered: Put all docs in `docs/adr/`. Rejected because existing ADR style is compact decision record, and settings/feature manuals would make ADRs noisy."}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_risks_trade_offs", "label": "Risks / Trade-offs", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 41", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "- Documentation drifts from implementation \u2192 Mitigation: settings doc cites `src/config.ts` and `src/types.ts` as source of truth; ADR requires checking specs/tests before updates. - Docs duplicate README content \u2192 Mitigation: new docs organize detailed references; README remains unchanged by this work because user constrained edits. - Settings reference misses nested keys \u2192 Mitigation: tasks require enumerating defaults from `DEFAULT_VIM_OPTIONS`, `DEFAULT_VIM_KEYMAP`, UI/search/macro/mark defa"}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_ref_src_config_ts", "label": "config.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_ref_src_types_ts", "label": "types.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_ref_docs_features_md", "label": "features.md", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_ref_docs_settings_md", "label": "settings.md", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_document", "target": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_context", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 1", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_document", "target": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_goals_non_goals", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 7", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_document", "target": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_decisions", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-05-29-document-pi-vimmode-features-settings/design.md", "source_location": "line 23", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_document", "target": "2026_05_29_document_pi_vimmode_features_settings_design_risks_trade_offs", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "so